title: Mune Sawagi RUSH RUSH RUSH!
original_name: 胸さわぎ RUSH 　 RUSH 　 RUSH!
sinopse: When Maiko was walking crying, a man suddenly appeared to give her some tissue. He is Ishida. First she thought he was a kind man, but he is a hell of a rude person. But she gets interested in him, and wants him to say "I love you". (Source: M-U)
